Name:		stella
Version:	1.3
Release:	1
License:	GPL
Group:		Applications/Emulators
Source0:	http://dl.sourceforge.net/stella/%{name}-%{version}-src.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	b9318f82a180ff0a404fca78511b2772
